From: LineageOS Desktop Project <noreply@local>
Subject: [PATCH] Launcher3: expose show-desktop toggle through SystemUiProxy

TaskbarNavButtonController routes the desktop taskbar spacer click through
SystemUiProxy. Keep the wrapper in a small follow-up patch so the large
Launcher3 patch does not need a second hunk in SystemUiProxy.kt after the
bubble-listener hunk has already shifted the file.

Applies on top of packages-apps-Launcher3.patch.

diff --git a/quickstep/src/com/android/quickstep/SystemUiProxy.kt b/quickstep/src/com/android/quickstep/SystemUiProxy.kt
--- a/quickstep/src/com/android/quickstep/SystemUiProxy.kt
+++ b/quickstep/src/com/android/quickstep/SystemUiProxy.kt
@@ -1310,6 +1310,12 @@ class SystemUiProxy @Inject constructor(
             )
         }
 
+    /** Toggle between showing the desktop and restoring previously visible desktop apps. */
+    fun toggleShowDesktop(displayId: Int) =
+        executeWithErrorLog({ "Failed call toggleShowDesktop" }) {
+            desktopMode?.toggleShowDesktop(displayId)
+        }
+
     /** If task with the given id is on the desktop, bring it to front */
     fun showDesktopApp(
         taskId: Int,
